701759f-a.title: Bronx: Secor Avenue - 233rd Street (East)
701759f-a.text:
(1)
3818 Secor Avenoe, east side, between E. 233rd Street and
Light Street, showing the Nativity of Our Blessed Lady Roman
Catholic Church. The view is southward.
May 16, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
A more distant view of the church as seen across E, 233rd
Street.
May 16, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
